commentary: Yadav to Tamim Iqbal, OUT first wicket of the series. Tamim's edgy innings ends. He is squared up by this shortish delivery that angles across him. Seems to have kissed the outside edge on the way. Well actually it hasn't. The bat hit the pad at the same time as the ball passed the bat, creating the misleading noise. Tamim has had a rough one here

commentary: Mashrafe Mortaza to Rahane, OUT there is life in this dog yet. Ziaur Rahamn, who was rather slow in diving a ball ago, flies at short third man to send Rahane back. Slower ball from Mortaza, Rahane drives, looking to go over extra, but gets a thick edge, and Zia takes it overhead when the ball has almost passed him
